---
// ============================================================
// carlitos.astro - Recibo de Remesa para AD GLOBAL SERVICES LLC
// Ubicación: src/pages/carlitos.astro
// Ruta local: http://localhost:4321/carlitos
// ============================================================
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Recibo de Transferencia - AD GLOBAL SERVICES LLC</title>
    <style>
        /* ===== RESET Y ESTILOS GENERALES ===== */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f4f6fa;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 30px 15px;
        }

        /* ===== TARJETA DEL RECIBO ===== */
        .recibo {
            max-width: 880px;
            width: 100%;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(109, 30, 209, 0.12);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #f0ebf7;
        }

        /* ===== BANDA SUPERIOR ===== */
        .banda-superior {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6d1ed1, #8b3ae8);
            padding: 14px 35px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .banda-superior .msb-tag {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 4px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .banda-superior .estado {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .banda-superior .estado .check {
            background: #4caf50;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        /* ===== CONTENIDO ===== */
        .contenido {
            padding: 28px 35px 22px 35px;
        }

        /* ===== ENCABEZADO ===== */
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            padding-bottom: 18px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0ebf7;
        }

        .header-izq {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .header-izq .logo {
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            object-fit: contain;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .header-izq .info-empresa .nombre {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #6d1ed1;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        }

        .header-izq .info-empresa .dir {
            font-size: 11.5px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 1px;
        }

        .header-izq .info-empresa .tel {
            font-size: 11.5px;
            color: #777;
        }

        .header-der {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .header-der .titulo {
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }

        .header-der .num-recibo {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6d1ed1;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #f4f0fc;
            padding: 2px 14px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 3px;
        }

        .header-der .fecha {
            font-size: 11.5px;
            color: #999;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        /* ===== KYC EN DOS COLUMNAS ===== */
        .kyc-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }

        .kyc-box {
            background: #f9f7fc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-left: 4px solid #6d1ed1;
        }

        .kyc-box h4 {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #6d1ed1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.6px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .kyc-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 3px 0;
            font-size: 12.5px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #eee;
        }

        .kyc-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .kyc-row .lbl {
            color: #999;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .kyc-row .val {
            color: #1a1a2e;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* ===== SECCIÓN MONTO ===== */
        .monto-box {
            background: #f9f7fc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .monto-box .titulo-monto {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #6d1ed1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.6px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .monto-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 4px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #eee;
        }

        .monto-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .monto-row .lbl {
            color: #888;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .monto-row .val {
            color: #1a1a2e;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .monto-row.total {
            border-top: 2px solid #d5c6ed;
            padding-top: 8px;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .monto-row.total .lbl {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .monto-row.total .val {
            font-size: 19px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #6d1ed1;
        }

        /* ===== TIPO DE CAMBIO ===== */
        .tc-box {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            background: #f4f0fc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .tc-item .tc-lbl {
            font-size: 10.5px;
            color: #999;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }

        .tc-item .tc-val {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #6d1ed1;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .tc-item .tc-val.dark {
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        /* ===== AVISO LEGAL - LETRA PEQUEÑA ===== */
        .legal-box {
            background: #faf9fd;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-left: 3px solid #6d1ed1;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .legal-box .legal-text {
            font-size: 10.5px;
            color: #777;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .legal-box .legal-text.en {
            margin-top: 6px;
            padding-top: 6px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e8e0f0;
        }

        .legal-box .legal-text strong {
            color: #555;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .legal-box .legal-text .highlight {
            color: #6d1ed1;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ===== DECLARACIÓN ===== */
        .declaracion {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            background: #faf9fd;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            border: 1px solid #ede8f5;
        }

        .declaracion .dec-item {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .declaracion .dec-item .dec-label {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #6d1ed1;
            display: block;
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .declaracion .dec-item.en {
            border-left: 1px solid #e0d8ed;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        /* ===== PIE ===== */
        .footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            padding-top: 14px;
            border-top: 2px solid #f0ebf7;
            font-size: 10.5px;
            color: #aaa;
        }

        .footer .regs {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 6px 16px;
        }

        .footer .regs .badge {
            background: #eef0f5;
            padding: 2px 10px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 9.5px;
        }

        .footer .copy {
            color: #bbb;
            font-size: 9.5px;
        }

        /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
        @media (max-width: 700px) {
            .banda-superior {
                padding: 12px 20px;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .contenido {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .header-der {
                text-align: left;
                width: 100%;
            }

            .kyc-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 12px;
            }

            .tc-box {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 6px;
            }

            .declaracion {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 6px;
            }

            .declaracion .dec-item.en {
                border-left: none;
                padding-left: 0;
                border-top: 1px solid #e0d8ed;
                padding-top: 6px;
            }

            .footer {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
        }

        @media print {
            body {
                background: #fff;
                padding: 0;
            }
            .recibo {
                box-shadow: none;
                border: 1px solid #ddd;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .banda-superior {
                border-radius: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="recibo">

        

        <!-- ===== CONTENIDO ===== -->
        <div class="contenido">

            <!-- ===== ENCABEZADO ===== -->
            <div class="header">
                <div class="header-izq">
                    <img src="/public/img/logo.webp" alt="AD GLOBAL SERVICES LLC" class="logo" />
                    <div class="info-empresa">
                        <span class="nombre">AD GLOBAL SERVICES LLC</span>
                        <br>
                        <span class="dir">7901 4th St N #25273 · St. Petersburg, FL 33702</span>
                        <span class="tel">📞 (448) 204-5984</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="header-der">
                    <div class="titulo">RECIBO</div>
                    <div class="num-recibo"># REM-2026-0001</div>
                    <div class="fecha">08 de julio de 2026 · 10:35 AM EST</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ===== KYC: REMITENTE Y DESTINATARIO ===== -->
            <div class="kyc-grid">

                <!-- Remitente -->
                <div class="kyc-box">
                    <h4>📤 Remitente / Sender</h4>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">Nombre</span>
                        <span class="val">Juan Pérez González</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">Documento</span>
                        <span class="val">Pasaporte · 123456789</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">Dirección</span>
                        <span class="val">123 Main St, Miami, FL 33101</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">Teléfono</span>
                        <span class="val">(305) 555-1234</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">Correo</span>
                        <span class="val">juan.perez@email.com</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">ID Cliente</span>
                        <span class="val">CL-98765</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Destinatario -->
                <div class="kyc-box">
                    <h4>📥 Destinatario / Recipient</h4>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">Nombre</span>
                        <span class="val">María López Hernández</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">País</span>
                        <span class="val">🇲🇽 México</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">Método de entrega</span>
                        <span class="val">Depósito bancario</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">Banco</span>
                        <span class="val">Banco de México · 123456789</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">Teléfono</span>
                        <span class="val">+52 55 1234 5678</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="kyc-row">
                        <span class="lbl">Relación</span>
                        <span class="val">Familiar</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- ===== DETALLE DE MONTO ===== -->
            <div class="monto-box">
                <div class="titulo-monto">💰 Detalle de la Transferencia</div>

                <div class="monto-row">
                    <span class="lbl">Monto enviado (USD)</span>
                    <span class="val">$1,200.00</span>
                </div>
                <div class="monto-row">
                    <span class="lbl">Comisión</span>
                    <span class="val">$15.00</span>
                </div>
                <div class="monto-row">
                    <span class="lbl">Impuestos</span>
                    <span class="val">$0.00</span>
                </div>
                <div class="monto-row total">
                    <span class="lbl">TOTAL A PAGAR</span>
                    <span class="val">$1,215.00</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ===== TIPO DE CAMBIO ===== -->
            <div class="tc-box">
                <div class="tc-item">
                    <div class="tc-lbl">Tipo de cambio</div>
                    <div class="tc-val">1 USD = 20.50 MXN</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tc-item">
                    <div class="tc-lbl">Monto a recibir</div>
                    <div class="tc-val dark">$24,600.00 MXN</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tc-item">
                    <div class="tc-lbl">Fecha de disponibilidad</div>
                    <div class="tc-val dark" style="font-size:15px;">08 de julio de 2026</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ===== AVISO LEGAL - LETRA PEQUEÑA ===== -->
            <div class="legal-box">

                <div class="legal-text">
                    <strong>⏳ Derecho a cancelar:</strong> Tiene <strong>30 minutos</strong> después de realizar el pago para cancelar la transferencia y recibir un reembolso completo, a menos que los fondos ya hayan sido recogidos o depositados en la cuenta del destinatario.<br />
                    <strong>📞 Disputas y errores:</strong> Para disputar un error, contacte a <span class="highlight">AD GLOBAL SERVICES LLC</span> al <strong>(448) 204-5984</strong> dentro de los <strong>190 días</strong> posteriores a la transacción.
                </div>

                <div class="legal-text en">
                    <strong>⏳ Right to Cancel:</strong> You have <strong>30 minutes</strong> after making the payment to cancel the transfer and receive a full refund, unless the funds have already been picked up or deposited into the recipient's account.<br />
                    <strong>📞 Disputes and Errors:</strong> To dispute an error, contact <span class="highlight">AD GLOBAL SERVICES LLC</span> at <strong>(448) 204-5984</strong> within <strong>190 days</strong> of the transaction.
                </div>

                <div style="height:1px; background:#e8e0f0; margin:8px 0;"></div>

                <div class="legal-text">
                    <strong>📜 AVISO LEGAL Y POLÍTICA DE PRIVACIDAD:</strong> Esta operación se ha realizado conforme a sus indicaciones, actuando usted por cuenta propia. Los datos proporcionados para llevar a cabo la transacción, así como una copia de la documentación que acredita su identidad, serán tratados por <span class="highlight">AD GLOBAL SERVICES LLC</span>, con domicilio en 7901 4th St N #25273, St. Petersburg, FL 33702, y número de registro MSB: MRX26-00003351, en calidad de responsable del tratamiento y con la finalidad de prestar el servicio de transferencia de remesas. De conformidad con la normativa vigente (Regla de Transferencias de Remesas del CFPB y Ley de Secreto Bancario - BSA), la Entidad ha procedido a conservar un registro electrónico íntegro del presente recibo y de sus datos personales. Para más información sobre el tratamiento de sus datos personales, consulte nuestra Política de Privacidad en nuestro sitio web.
                </div>

                <div class="legal-text en">
                    <strong>📜 LEGAL NOTICE AND PRIVACY POLICY:</strong> This transaction has been carried out according to your instructions, acting on your own behalf. The data provided to carry out the transaction, as well as a copy of the documentation verifying your identity, will be processed by <span class="highlight">AD GLOBAL SERVICES LLC</span>, with registered address at 7901 4th St N #25273, St. Petersburg, FL 33702, and MSB Registration Number: MRX26-00003351, as data controller and for the purpose of providing the remittance transfer service. In accordance with applicable regulations (CFPB Remittance Transfer Rule and Bank Secrecy Act - BSA), the Entity has retained a complete electronic record of this receipt and your personal data. For more information about the processing of your personal data, please refer to our Privacy Policy on our website.
                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- ===== DECLARACIÓN DEL CLIENTE ===== -->
            <div class="declaracion">
                <div class="dec-item">
                    <span class="dec-label">✍️ Declaración del Cliente</span>
                    El remitente declara explícitamente que esta transacción se realiza en su propio nombre y que la información proporcionada es veraz y completa.
                </div>
                <div class="dec-item en">
                    <span class="dec-label">✍️ Client Declaration</span>
                    The sender explicitly declares that this transaction is performed on his/her own behalf and that the information provided is truthful and complete.
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ===== PIE DE PÁGINA ===== -->
            <div class="footer">
                <div class="regs">
                    <span>🛡️ <span class="badge">CFPB</span> (855) 411-2372</span>
                    <span>🛡️ <span class="badge">OFR Florida</span> www.flofr.gov</span>
                    <span>🛡️ <span class="badge">FinCEN</span> www.fincen.gov</span>
                </div>
                <span class="copy">AD GLOBAL SERVICES LLC · MSB # MRX26-00003351 · Documento legal</span>
            </div>

        </div><!-- fin .contenido -->

    </div><!-- fin .recibo -->

</body>
</html>